  "title": "feat(ui-components): introduce `Carousel`",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nThis PR introduces the Carousel UI component. It is a port of the HorizontalSlider component designed. There are a few changes:\r\n\r\n- HorizontalSlider is now named Carousel, obv\r\n- Class names are prefixed with `ais-Carousel`\r\n- References are not forwarded anymore, `Renderer` is extended to allow flavors to provide their `useRef` implementation\r\n- Carousel CSS colors are now SCSS variables instead of CSS variables\r\n\r\nThis PR does not implement the Carousel as a built-in layout in any InstantSearch widget for now.\r\n\r\n[**Preview →**](https://kq8txk.csb.app/)\r\n\r\n**Before merging**\r\n\r\n- [x] Remove carousel import in algolia and reset SCSS files\r\n- [x] Remove changes to getting started\r\n\r\nFX-2817",
